text: Trump, Biden both said People are dying that have never died before
Quotes Joe Biden as saying people who have never died before are now dying from coronavirus.
An image shared on Facebook more than 200 times claims former Vice President Joe Biden said, People who have never died before are now dying from corona virus [sic].
A viral Facebook post shared over 18,000 times claims Democratic presidential nominee Joe Biden said that if he was president, there would have been zero COVID-19 deaths.
A Fox News chyron reported Joe Biden has been president for nine hours and 400,000 people are dead.
Half of the votes for Joe Biden in the 2020 presidential election are from dead people.
